sequenceDiagram
    participant Alice as Alice (Client)
    participant Server as Server (HTTPS)
    participant Bob as Bob (Client)
    
    Note over Alice,Bob: REGISTRATION
    Alice->>Alice: Generate RSA Keys
    Alice->>Server: POST /register
    Server->>Server: Hash password (bcrypt)
    Server-->>Alice: 200 OK
    
    Note over Alice,Bob: LOGIN
    Alice->>Server: POST /login
    Server->>Server: Verify password
    Server-->>Alice: {session_token}
    
    Note over Alice,Bob: SEND MESSAGE
    Alice->>Server: GET /public_key/bob
    Server-->>Alice: {bob_public_key}
    Alice->>Alice: Encrypt with AES-GCM
    Alice->>Alice: Encrypt AES key with RSA
    Alice->>Server: POST /send (encrypted)
    Server->>Server: Store encrypted
    
    Note over Alice,Bob: RECEIVE MESSAGE
    Bob->>Server: GET /messages
    Server-->>Bob: [encrypted messages]
    Bob->>Bob: Decrypt with RSA + AES
    Bob->>Bob: Display plaintext